00:30:26,585 --> 00:30:30,288
Thank you for keeping this between us. Hmm?

619
00:30:33,192 --> 00:30:35,093
Of course.

620
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:39,097
I'll just...

621
00:30:41,767 --> 00:30:43,835
Go.

