Who's that?

691
00:34:42,908 --> 00:34:43,941
No idea.

692
00:34:49,615 --> 00:34:50,715
Professor.

693
00:34:53,018 --> 00:34:54,852
Get the hell out!

694
00:34:55,921 --> 00:34:57,788
